kesa hajimete omotta 
maegami ga osana sa o nokoshiteru genin na no ne 
kakko kawaii fuku o kite mitara 
dekiru kanji ja nakute se mo tari nakatta 

kitto mitame bakari o ki ni shitetemo 
nakami migaka nakya 

otona ni naritakute senobi o shite mo 
neru toki no taoru hanasenai kara 
otona ni naru koto tsuyoku naru koto 
arinomama mireru koto

kinou oroshita kutsu wa itakutte 
akaku natta tokoro ga sabishiku mieteru 

heya ni modotta ato wa 
hitori goto itte wa terebi o mite warattari shiteru 
sukoshi kaketa tsume mite omoidasu 
kan koohii akerarenai yurusareru josei 

kitto kokochi yo sa dake motometetemo 
tarinai mono ga aru 

otona ni naritakute senobi o shite mo 
ude makura no mama nemurenai kara 
otona ni naru koto hitori shiru koto 
arinomama ireru koto 

otona ni naritakute senobi o shite mo 
neru toki no taoru hanasenai kara 
otona ni naru koto tsuyoku naru koto 
arinomama mireru koto

kinou oroshita kutsu wa itai kedo 
akaku najimeru you ni kyou mo haite ikou
